{"type":"message","id":"73d4e37e","parentId":"b8f9f4b9","timestamp":"2026-03-15T20:04:36.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到有一个完整的 Notion 主题包，包含：\n- 壁纸文件\n- Rainmeter 皮肤\n- 安装脚本\n- TranslucentTB 设置\n- README\n\n壁纸在注册表中已经设置了，但用户说壁纸没有变化。这可能是因为：\n1. 系统没有刷新壁纸\n2. 需要用户重新登录或重启\n\n让我先读取 README 和安装脚本，了解完整的安装步骤，然后执行完整的美化流程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！主题包已经存在。让我读取 README 和安装脚本，了解完整流程。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf319bab19e8346e4afdc97ad1a25","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf319bc9c6bb2d5921754fa19e416","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\install.ps1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":687,"output":264,"cacheRead":15680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773605070692}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b39cbd1","parentId":"73d4e37e","timestamp":"2026-03-15T20:04:36.660Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf319bab19e8346e4afdc97ad1a25","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 🖤 Notion Style Theme\n\n让你的 Windows 桌面变成 Notion 风格：极简、高效、好看。\n\n---\n\n## 📁 目录结构\n\n```\nNotion-Theme/\n├── install.ps1              # 主安装脚本\n├── set-wallpaper.ps1        # 快速切换壁纸\n├── wallpapers/\n│   ├── notion-dark.png      # 深黑纯色\n│   ├── notion-light.png     # 奶白纯色\n│   └── notion-gradient.png  # 深色渐变\n└── rainmeter-skins/\n    └── NotionStyle/\n        ├── NotionStyle.ini       # 深色主题\n        └── NotionStyle-Light.ini # 浅色主题\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n### 步骤 1: 安装软件\n\n需要安装两个软件：\n\n| 软件 | 用途 | 下载链接 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **Rainmeter** | 桌面小部件 | [官网](https://www.rainmeter.net/) |\n| **TranslucentTB** | 任务栏透明 | [GitHub](https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases) |\n\n或运行脚本自动下载：\n```powershell\n.\\install.ps1 -InstallApps\n```\n\n### 步骤 2: 设置壁纸\n\n```powershell\n# 深色壁纸（推荐）\n.\\set-wallpaper.ps1 -Theme dark\n\n# 浅色壁纸\n.\\set-wallpaper.ps1 -Theme light\n\n# 渐变壁纸\n.\\set-wallpaper.ps1 -Theme gradient\n```\n\n### 步骤 3: 安装 Rainmeter 皮肤\n\n```powershell\n.\\install.ps1 -InstallRainmeterSkin\n```\n\n然后在 Rainmeter 中：\n1. 右键托盘图标 → 管理皮肤\n2. 展开 `NotionStyle` 文件夹\n3. 加载 `NotionStyle.ini`（深色）或 `NotionStyle-Light.ini`（浅色）\n\n### 步骤 4: 配置 TranslucentTB\n\n启动 TranslucentDB，然后在托盘图标右键：\n- 选择 **Clear**（完全透明）或 **Normal**（带模糊）\n- 勾选 **Open at boot**（开机自启）\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 自定义\n\n### 修改待办事项\n\n编辑皮肤文件，找到 `[Todo1]`、`[Todo2]` 等区块：\n```ini\n[Todo1]\nText=☐ 你的任务内容\n```\n\n### 修改快捷方式\n\n找到 `[LinkXXX]` 区块，修改路径：\n```ini\n[LinkVSCode]\nText=💻 VS Code\nLeftMouseUpAction=[\"你的程序路径\"]\n```\n\n### 修改颜色\n\n在皮肤文件顶部找到 `[Variables]` 区块：\n```ini\nTextColor=#FAFAF9     ; 主文字颜色\nAccentColor=#2EAADC   ; 强调色\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📦 推荐搭配\n\n| 项目 | 推荐 |\n|------|------|\n| 图标 | Papirus, WhiteSur, Nord |\n| 窗口主题 | SecureUxTheme + 简约主题 |\n| 字体 | Microsoft YaHei UI, Inter, Noto Sans |\n| 浏览器主题 | Notion 风格扩展 |\n\n---\n\n## ⌨️ 快捷命令\n\n```powershell\n# 完整安装\n.\\install.ps1 -InstallApps -SetWallpaper -InstallRainmeterSkin\n\n# 只换壁纸\n.\\set-wallpaper.ps1 -Theme dark\n\n# 只装皮肤\n.\\install.ps1 -InstallRainmeterSkin\n```\n\n---\n\n享受你的 Notion 风格桌面！🖤\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773605076659}}
{"type":"message","id":"36cb9233","parentId":"2b39cbd1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T20:04:36.662Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf319bc9c6bb2d5921754fa19e416","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env pwsh\n# ============================================\n# Notion Theme 安装脚本\n# 一键美化你的 Windows\n# ============================================\n\nparam(\n    [switch]$InstallApps,\n    [switch]$SetWallpaper,\n    [switch]$InstallRainmeterSkin\n)\n\n$ThemeDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\n$WallpaperDir = \"$ThemeDir\\wallpapers\"\n\nWrite-Host @\"\n\n╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║           🖤 Notion Style Theme Installer                ║\n║           极简 · 高效 · 美学                             ║\n╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\n\"@ -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 检查目录\nif (-not (Test-Path $ThemeDir)) {\n    Write-Host \"[✗] 未找到主题目录: $ThemeDir\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# 1. 安装软件\n# ============================================\nif ($InstallApps) {\n    Write-Host \"`n📦 正在安装必要软件...`n\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    \n    # 检查 Rainmeter\n    $rainmeter = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n                 Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*Rainmeter*\" }\n    \n    if (-not $rainmeter) {\n        Write-Host \"  下载 Rainmeter...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n        $rainmeterUrl = \"https://github.com/rainmeter/rainmeter/releases/download/v4.5.18.3762/Rainmeter-4.5.18.3762.exe\"\n        $rainmeterPath = \"$ThemeDir\\rainmeter-installer.exe\"\n        \n        try {\n            Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $rainmeterUrl -OutFile $rainmeterPath -UseBasicParsing\n            Write-Host \"  [✓] Rainmeter 下载完成\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-Host \"  [!] 请手动运行: $rainmeterPath\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        } catch {\n            Write-Host \"  [✗] Rainmeter 下载失败，请手动下载:\" -ForegroundColor Red\n            Write-Host \"      https://www.rainmeter.net/\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"  [✓] Rainmeter 已安装\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    }\n    \n    # 检查 TranslucentTB\n    $translucent = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n                   Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*TranslucentTB*\" }\n    \n    if (-not $translucent) {\n        Write-Host \"  下载 TranslucentTB...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n        $tbUrl = \"https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/download/2024.1/TranslucentTB.Setup.exe\"\n        $tbPath = \"$ThemeDir\\translucenttb-installer.exe\"\n        \n        try {\n            Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $tbUrl -OutFile $tbPath -UseBasicParsing\n            Write-Host \"  [✓] TranslucentTB 下载完成\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-Host \"  [!] 请手动运行: $tbPath\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        } catch {\n            Write-Host \"  [✗] TranslucentTB 下载失败，请手动下载:\" -ForegroundColor Red\n            Write-Host \"      https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"  [✓] TranslucentTB 已安装\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    }\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# 2. 设置壁纸\n# ============================================\nif ($SetWallpaper) {\n    Write-Host \"`n🖼️ 设置壁纸...`n\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    \n    $wallpaperPath = \"$WallpaperDir\\notion-dark.png\"\n    \n    if (Test-Path $wallpaperPath) {\n        # 设置壁纸\n        Add-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\n\npublic class Wallpaper {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto)]\n    public static extern int SystemParametersInfo(int uAction, int uParam, string lpvParam, int fuWinIni);\n    \n    public static void Set(string path) {\n        SystemParametersInfo(20, 0, path, 3);\n    }\n}\n\"@\n        [Wallpaper]::Set($wallpaperPath)\n        Write-Host \"  [✓] 壁纸已设置\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"  [!] 壁纸文件不存在，请先创建壁纸\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        Write-Host \"      提示: 将纯色图片保存到 $wallpaperPath\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    }\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# 3. 安装 Rainmeter 皮肤\n# ============================================\nif ($InstallRainmeterSkin) {\n    Write-Host \"`n🎨 安装 Rainmeter 皮肤...`n\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    \n    $skinsDest = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\"\n    $skinsSource = \"$ThemeDir\\rainmeter-skins\\NotionStyle\"\n    \n    if (Test-Path $skinsSource) {\n        # 复制皮肤文件\n        if (Test-Path $skinsDest) {\n            Remove-Item $skinsDest -Recurse -Force\n        }\n        Copy-Item $skinsSource -Destination $skinsDest -Recurse -Force\n        Write-Host \"  [✓] 皮肤已安装到: $skinsDest\" -ForegroundColor Green\n        \n        # 刷新 Rainmeter\n        $rainmeterProcess = Get-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        if ($rainmeterProcess) {\n            Start-Process -FilePath \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\" -ArgumentList \"!Refresh *\"\n            Write-Host \"  [✓] Rainmeter 已刷新\" -ForegroundColor Green\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"  [!] Rainmeter 未运行，请先启动\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"  [✗] 皮肤源文件不存在\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# 完成\n# ============================================\nWrite-Host @\"\n\n╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n║                    ✅ 安装完成！                         ║\n╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣\n║  后续步骤:                                               ║\n║                                                          ║\n║  1. 打开 Rainmeter → 加载 NotionStyle 皮肤              ║\n║  2. 启动 TranslucentTB → 设置任务栏透明                  ║\n║  3. 右键皮肤 → 编辑 → 自定义待办事项和快捷方式           ║\n║                                                          ║\n║  📁 主题目录: $ThemeDir\n╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\n\"@ -ForegroundColor Cyan\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773605076661}}
{"type":"message","id":"111792a4","parentId":"36cb9233","timestamp":"2026-03-15T20:04:56.977Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在了解了整个主题包的结构。让我检查一下当前系统的状态：\n\n1. 壁纸 - 注册表已设置，但可能没有生效（需要刷新）\n2. Rainmeter - 是否安装？\n3. TranslucentTB - 是否安装？\n\n让我检查这些软件的安装状态，然后执行完整的安装流程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！让我检查当前系统状态，然后逐步完成美化。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf319efb9f0c3c4ff313e8c40638b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 Rainmeter 是否安装\n$r = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\", \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\WOW6432Node\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*Rainmeter*\" }\nif ($r) { \"Rainmeter: 已安装\" } else { \"Rainmeter: 未安装\" }\n\n# 检查 TranslucentTB 是否安装\n$t = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\", \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\WOW6432Node\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*TranslucentTB*\" }\nif ($t) { \"TranslucentTB: 已安装\" } else { \"TranslucentTB: 未安装\" }\n\n# 检查 Rainmeter 进程\n$p = Get-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($p) { \"Rainmeter 进程: 运行中\" } else { \"Rainmeter 进程: 未运行\" }\n\n# 检查 TranslucentTB 进程\n$tbp = Get-Process -Name \"TranslucentTB\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($tbp) { \"TranslucentTB 进程: 运行中\" } else { \"TranslucentTB 进程: 未运行\" }\n\n# 检查皮肤是否已安装\n$skinPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\"\nif (Test-Path $skinPath) { \"Rainmeter 皮肤: 已安装\" } else { \"Rainmeter 皮肤: 未安装\" }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":2656,"output":545,"cacheRead":16320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19521,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773605076662}}
