{"type":"message","id":"8df6aacb","parentId":"13b809e1","timestamp":"2026-03-15T20:10:51.717Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"皮肤已经在配置中了！`Active=1` 表示皮肤已加载。现在让我确认一下所有步骤都完成了，并设置开机自启动。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"皮肤已加载！让我设置开机自启动："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf31f62e25cee5cd0504b2997b627","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 设置 TranslucentTB 开机自启动\n$tbExe = \"C:\\Program Files\\WindowsApps\\28017CharlesMilette.TranslucentTB_2026.1.0.0_x64__v826wp6bftszj\\TranslucentTB.exe\"\n$startupFolder = \"$env:APPDATA\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Start Menu\\Programs\\Startup\"\n$shortcutPath = \"$startupFolder\\TranslucentTB.lnk\"\n\n# 创建快捷方式\n$WshShell = New-Object -ComObject WScript.Shell\n$shortcut = $WshShell.CreateShortcut($shortcutPath)\n$shortcut.TargetPath = $tbExe\n$shortcut.Save()\n\"TranslucentTB 开机自启动已设置\"\n\n# 检查 Rainmeter 的开机自启动\n$rmStartup = \"$startupFolder\\Rainmeter.lnk\"\nif (Test-Path $rmStartup) {\n    \"Rainmeter 开机自启动已存在\"\n} else {\n    $rmPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\"\n    $shortcut = $WshShell.CreateShortcut($rmStartup)\n    $shortcut.TargetPath = $rmPath\n    $shortcut.Save()\n    \"Rainmeter 开机自启动已设置\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":207,"output":342,"cacheRead":29312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29861,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773605429111}}
