{"type":"message","id":"27ece88d","parentId":"c745ff20","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:18:27.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说没有变化，我的美化太粗糙了，想要回滚然后尝试别的方案。\n\n我需要：\n1. 回滚所有更改 - 恢复原始壁纸，停止/卸载 Rainmeter 和 TranslucentTB\n2. 然后讨论其他美化方案\n\n让我先回滚。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，让我帮你回滚所有更改。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4ddb288bf81b83a7c10f178b755","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 停止 Rainmeter\nStop-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\"Rainmeter 已停止\"\n\n# 停止 TranslucentTB\nStop-Process -Name \"TranslucentTB\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\"TranslucentTB 已停止\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4ddb8732d5f554fa97ff7ca5cca","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 恢复默认壁纸（Windows 默认蓝色）\n$defaultWallpaper = \"C:\\Windows\\Web\\Wallpaper\\Windows\\img0.jpg\"\nif (-not (Test-Path $defaultWallpaper)) {\n    # 或者用纯色背景\n    $defaultWallpaper = \"\"\n}\n\nAdd-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\n\npublic class Wallpaper {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto)]\n    public static extern int SystemParametersInfo(int uAction, int uParam, string lpvParam, int fuWinIni);\n    \n    public static void Set(string path) {\n        SystemParametersInfo(20, 0, path, 3);\n    }\n}\n\"@\n\nif ($defaultWallpaper -and (Test-Path $defaultWallpaper)) {\n    [Wallpaper]::Set($defaultWallpaper)\n    \"壁纸已恢复为: $defaultWallpaper\"\n} else {\n    # 设置为纯色背景（深蓝色）\n    Set-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"Wallpaper\" -Value \"\" -Force\n    Set-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Colors\" -Name \"Background\" -Value \"0 0 0\" -Force\n    [Wallpaper]::Set(\"\")\n    \"壁纸已清除，恢复为纯色背景\"\n}"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4ddd0d86aad4648ba5aa571f66d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 删除 Rainmeter 皮肤\n$skinPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\"\nif (Test-Path $skinPath) {\n    Remove-Item $skinPath -Recurse -Force\n    \"Rainmeter NotionStyle 皮肤已删除\"\n}\n\n# 删除 Rainmeter 配置\n$rmIni = \"$env:APPDATA\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.ini\"\nif (Test-Path $rmIni) {\n    Remove-Item $rmIni -Force\n    \"Rainmeter 配置已删除\"\n}"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4dddc46ed7265658f656b2dbe59","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 卸载 TranslucentTB\nwinget uninstall --id CharlesMilette.TranslucentTB --silent 2>$null\n\"TranslucentTB 卸载命令已执行\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":20504,"output":685,"cacheRead":9792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30981,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773634678664}}
