{"type":"message","id":"4cd53cd2","parentId":"7155e22a","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:22:05.439Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，当前壁纸是 Windows 默认壁纸，Rainmeter 和 TranslucentTB 都没有运行。壁纸文件存在，大小 17896 bytes，看起来是个小图片（可能是纯色图片）。\n\n让我先设置壁纸，用更可靠的方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4e10aa2d7e2be7eb0528500a8bb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 方法1：用 PowerShell 设置壁纸并立即刷新\nAdd-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\nusing System.Drawing;\n\npublic class Wallpaper {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto)]\n    public static extern int SystemParametersInfo(int uAction, int uParam, string lpvParam, int fuWinIni);\n    \n    public static void Set(string path, int style = 2) {\n        // SPI_SETDESKWALLPAPER = 20\n        // SPIF_UPDATEINIFILE = 0x01\n        // SPIF_SENDWININICHANGE = 0x02\n        SystemParametersInfo(20, style, path, 3);\n    }\n}\n\"@\n\n$wallpaper = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\"\n\n# 设置注册表\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"Wallpaper\" -Value $wallpaper -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"WallpaperStyle\" -Value \"10\" -Force  # 填充\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"TileWallpaper\" -Value \"0\" -Force\n\n# 调用 API\n[Wallpaper]::Set($wallpaper)\n\n# 广播设置变更\nAdd-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\n\npublic class WallpaperBroadcast {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto)]\n    public static extern IntPtr SendMessage(IntPtr hWnd, int Msg, IntPtr wParam, IntPtr lParam);\n    \n    public static void Refresh() {\n        // HWND_BROADCAST = 0xFFFF\n        // WM_SETTINGCHANGE = 0x1A\n        SendMessage((IntPtr)0xFFFF, 0x1A, IntPtr.Zero, IntPtr.Zero);\n    }\n}\n\"@\n[WallpaperBroadcast]::Refresh()\n\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 1\n\n# 验证\n$wp = Get-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name Wallpaper\n\"注册表壁纸: $($wp.Wallpaper)\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":600,"output":564,"cacheRead":32512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33676,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773634884968}}
