{"type":"message","id":"7b44f488","parentId":"737396f7","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:25:26.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我用更简单的方法——直接用 RUNDLL32 来设置壁纸。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4e42fa7364b03678dd7e6bba0a2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 使用更简单的方法设置壁纸\n$wallpaper = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\"\n\n# 设置注册表\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"Wallpaper\" -Value $wallpaper -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"WallpaperStyle\" -Value \"10\" -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"TileWallpaper\" -Value \"0\" -Force\n\n# 用 rundll32 刷新\nrundll32.exe user32.dll,UpdatePerUserSystemParameters\n\n# 等待一下\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\n\n# 验证\n$wp = Get-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name Wallpaper\nWrite-Host \"注册表壁纸已设置为: $($wp.Wallpaper)\"\n\n# 刷新桌面\n$shell = New-Object -ComObject Shell.Application\n$null = $shell.Windows().Item(0).Refresh()\nWrite-Host \"桌面刷新命令已发送\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":99,"output":284,"cacheRead":33728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34111,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773635094067}}
{"type":"message","id":"105cf635","parentId":"7b44f488","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:25:29.928Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf4e42fa7364b03678dd7e6bba0a2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ע�����ֽ������Ϊ: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\n���ܶ� Null ֵ����ʽ���÷�����\r\n����λ�� ��:21 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ $null = $shell.Windows().Item(0).Refresh()\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) []��RuntimeException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvokeMethodOnNull\r\n \r\n����ˢ�������ѷ���"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3245,"aggregated":"ע�����ֽ������Ϊ: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\n���ܶ� Null ֵ����ʽ���÷�����\r\n����λ�� ��:21 �ַ�: 1\r\n+ $null = $shell.Windows().Item(0).Refresh()\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) []��RuntimeException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvokeMethodOnNull\r\n \r\n����ˢ�������ѷ���","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773635129927}}
{"type":"message","id":"f040ec6a","parentId":"105cf635","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:27:20.215Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"注册表已经设置了，虽然桌面刷新命令出了点问题。让我尝试用一个更可靠的方式来刷新壁纸——通过重新启动 explorer.exe 或者使用控制面板的方式。\n\n不过，让我先确认用户能看到的桌面壁纸是否真的没变化。我可以让用户确认一下，或者强制刷新。\n\n实际上，Windows 设置壁纸的方式有几种：\n1. SystemParametersInfo API\n2. 注册表 + 刷新\n3. 通过 Shell 应用程序接口\n\n让我用另一种方式 - 通过 cmd 命令或者 PowerShell 的不同方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"注册表已设置。让我强制刷新桌面让壁纸生效："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4e5e9abe69034b8c0f2dd3f9231","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 强制刷新壁纸的多种方法\n\n# 方法1: 通过控制面板命令\ncontrol.exe desktop\n\nStart-Sleep -Milliseconds 500\n\n# 关闭控制面板窗口\nStop-Process -Name \"control\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\nWrite-Host \"已调用桌面设置刷新\"\n\n# 方法2: 强制广播 WM_SETTINGCHANGE\n$code = @'\n[DllImport(\"user32.dll\", SetLastError = true, CharSet = CharSet.Auto)]\npublic static extern IntPtr SendMessageTimeout(\n    IntPtr hWnd, int Msg, IntPtr wParam, string lParam,\n    uint fuFlags, uint uTimeout, out IntPtr lpdwResult);\n\npublic static void RefreshWallpaper() {\n    IntPtr result;\n    // HWND_BROADCAST = 0xFFFF, WM_SETTINGCHANGE = 0x1A\n    SendMessageTimeout((IntPtr)0xFFFF, 0x1A, IntPtr.Zero, \"Environment\", 0x0002, 5000, out result);\n}\n'@\nAdd-Type -MemberDefinition $code -Name \"Win32\" -Namespace \"Wallpaper\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n[Wallpaper.Win32]::RefreshWallpaper()\n\nWrite-Host \"壁纸刷新命令执行完成\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":424,"output":487,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34703,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773635129929}}
