{"type":"message","id":"66e5dc5b","parentId":"8ccf9f79","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:28:11.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"命令执行了，但我不确定壁纸是否真的变了。让我检查一下当前的壁纸状态，并询问用户是否看到了变化。\n\n其实，更好的方式是用一个可靠的方法来设置壁纸。让我试试用批处理文件或者更直接的方式。\n\n或者，让我先检查壁纸是否真的没有变化，可能用户需要的只是一个桌面刷新。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf4e6b9355a34872f5a5abbd350db","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查当前壁纸状态\nWrite-Host \"=== 壁纸状态检查 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 注册表\n$wp = Get-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name Wallpaper\nWrite-Host \"注册表值: $($wp.Wallpaper)\"\n\n# 文件是否存在\nif (Test-Path $wp.Wallpaper) {\n    Write-Host \"文件状态: 存在\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"文件状态: 不存在\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}\n\n# 尝试用 PowerShell 5.1 的内置方法\n$wallpaperPath = $wp.Wallpaper\nWrite-Host \"`n现在请确认：桌面壁纸是否已变成深黑色背景？\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":445,"output":301,"cacheRead":34176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34922,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773635242173}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd3aba9c","parentId":"66e5dc5b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:28:12.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf4e6b9355a34872f5a5abbd350db","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ��ֽ״̬��� ===\nע���ֵ: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\n�ļ�״̬: ����\n\n������ȷ�ϣ������ֽ�Ƿ��ѱ�����ɫ������"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1147,"aggregated":"=== ��ֽ״̬��� ===\nע���ֵ: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\n�ļ�״̬: ����\n\n������ȷ�ϣ������ֽ�Ƿ��ѱ�����ɫ������","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773635292410}}
