{"type":"message","id":"02fc3f21","parentId":"1bc4796b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:10:18.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要的是 Notion 的手绘风格，而不是简单的深色壁纸。之前我设置的只是纯色壁纸，这并不是 Notion 的标志性风格。\n\nNotion 的手绘风格通常包括：\n1. 手绘插画风格的壁纸（比如 Notion 官网的那些涂鸦风格插画）\n2. 简约的线条、手写字体\n3. 可爱的手绘图标\n4. 笔记本/素描纸的质感\n\n让我重新理解需求，需要：\n1. 找到或创建真正符合 Notion 手绘风格的壁纸\n2. 可能需要自定义 Rainmeter 皮肤使用手写字体和手绘风格元素\n\n让我先搜索一下 Notion 风格的手绘壁纸资源。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！你要的是 Notion 那种**手绘涂鸦风格**，就像 Notion 官网那种简约线条、可爱插画的感觉，而不是纯黑色背景。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf50d5483b6057aa5e9ccfb2ec24f","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Notion style hand drawn doodle wallpaper aesthetic illustration","count":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":24757,"output":365,"cacheRead":9920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35042,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773637808770}}
