{"type":"message","id":"b2e0c645","parentId":"e9be5d48","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:11:11.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Browser is also not available. Let me think about what I can do:\n\n1. Notion's hand-drawn style typically features:\n   - Simple line drawings\n   - Pastel colors or monochrome\n   - Notebook/sketchbook texture\n   - Handwritten fonts\n   - Cute doodles (stars, arrows, shapes)\n\n2. I can create a custom wallpaper using PowerShell and .NET to draw something in that style\n\n3. Or I can look for resources in the existing theme package\n\nLet me check what's in the wallpapers folder and also try to create a proper hand-drawn style wallpaper programmatically.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我看看现有壁纸，然后为你创建真正的 Notion 手绘风格壁纸："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf50e21865343bf2f2a78a133ab44","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf50e23b2de5db3d41fc2b7032381","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-gradient.png"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf50e25f4cec34b9814da623c6d04","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-light.png"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":158,"output":355,"cacheRead":34944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35457,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773637838410}}
