{"type":"message","id":"30ece826","parentId":"d0c75e44","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:12:03.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the wallpapers now:\n1. notion-dark.png - just a plain dark gray/solid color\n2. notion-gradient.png - has a subtle gradient\n3. notion-light.png - plain light/white background\n\nThese are NOT hand-drawn style at all - they're just solid colors or gradients. The user wants actual Notion-style hand-drawn illustrations - the cute doodles, lines, arrows, sketches that Notion is known for.\n\nI need to:\n1. Create a proper hand-drawn style wallpaper with Notion aesthetic\n2. This could include:\n   - Light paper texture background\n   - Hand-drawn style doodles (arrows, stars, shapes)\n   - Simple line art\n   - Maybe some \"sketchbook\" feel\n\nLet me create a proper Notion-style hand-drawn wallpaper programmatically using PowerShell with .NET drawing, or find a way to get proper resources.\n\nActually, let me create a custom wallpaper that captures the Notion hand-drawn aesthetic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了 — 现有的壁纸只是纯色和渐变，完全没有手绘风格！\n\n让我为你创建真正的 Notion 手绘风格壁纸："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf50e4cc55477fb0952822fd020ec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 创建 Notion 风格手绘壁纸\nAdd-Type -AssemblyName System.Drawing\n\n$width = 2560\n$height = 1440\n\n# 创建画布\n$bmp = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap($width, $height)\n$g = [System.Drawing.Graphics]::FromImage($bmp)\n$g.SmoothingMode = [System.Drawing.Drawing2D.SmoothingMode]::AntiAlias\n\n# 背景 - 温暖的米色/纸质感\n$bgColor = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(250, 247, 242)  # 暖白色纸质感\n$g.Clear($bgColor)\n\n# 定义画笔\n$gray = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(120, 120, 120)\n$lightGray = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(200, 200, 200)\n$accent = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(80, 80, 80)\n$blue = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(100, 150, 200)\n$orange = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(230, 180, 100)\n\n# 创建手绘风格的画笔（模拟铅笔/马克笔）\n$pen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen($gray, 3)\n$pen.EndCap = [System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LineCap]::Round\n$pen.StartCap = [System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LineCap]::Round\n\n$thinPen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen($lightGray, 2)\n$thinPen.EndCap = [System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LineCap]::Round\n\n# 添加淡淡的网格线（像笔记本）\n$gridPen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen([System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(235, 232, 227), 1)\nfor ($x = 0; $x -lt $width; $x += 40) {\n    $g.DrawLine($gridPen, $x, 0, $x, $height)\n}\nfor ($y = 0; $y -lt $height; $y += 40) {\n    $g.DrawLine($gridPen, 0, $y, $width, $y)\n}\n\n# 手绘风格的函数\nfunction Draw-WavyLine {\n    param($g, $pen, $x1, $y1, $x2, $y2)\n    $points = @()\n    $steps = 20\n    for ($i = 0; $i -le $steps; $i++) {\n        $t = $i / $steps\n        $x = $x1 + ($x2 - $x1) * $t\n        $y = $y1 + ($y2 - $y1) * $t + (Get-Random -Minimum -3 -Maximum 3)\n        $points += [System.Drawing.PointF]::new($x, $y)\n    }\n    if ($points.Count -gt 1) {\n        $g.DrawLines($pen, $points)\n    }\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Circle {\n    param($g, $pen, $cx, $cy, $r)\n    # 手绘圆 - 不完美的圆\n    $points = @()\n    for ($i = 0; $i -le 40; $i++) {\n        $angle = [Math]::PI * 2 * $i / 40\n        $rr = $r + (Get-Random -Minimum -5 -Maximum 5)\n        $x = $cx + $rr * [Math]::Cos($angle)\n        $y = $cy + $rr * [Math]::Sin($angle)\n        $points += [System.Drawing.PointF]::new($x, $y)\n    }\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $points)\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Checkmark {\n    param($g, $pen, $x, $y, $size)\n    $points = @(\n        [System.Drawing.Point]::new($x, $y + $size * 0.5),\n        [System.Drawing.Point]::new($x + $size * 0.35, $y + $size),\n        [System.Drawing.Point]::new($x + $size, $y)\n    )\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $points)\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Star {\n    param($g, $pen, $cx, $cy, $r)\n    $points = @()\n    for ($i = 0; $i -lt 10; $i++) {\n        $angle = [Math]::PI * 2 * $i / 10 - [Math]::PI / 2\n        $rr = if ($i % 2 -eq 0) { $r } else { $r * 0.4 }\n        $x = $cx + $rr * [Math]::Cos($angle)\n        $y = $cy + $rr * [Math]::Sin($angle)\n        $points += [System.Drawing.PointF]::new($x, $y)\n    }\n    $points += $points[0]\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $points)\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Arrow {\n    param($g, $pen, $x1, $y1, $x2, $y2, $size)\n    Draw-WavyLine $g $pen $x1 $y1 $x2 $y2\n    $angle = [Math]::Atan2($y2 - $y1, $x2 - $x1)\n    $arrowAngle = 0.5\n    $ax1 = $x2 - $size * [Math]::Cos($angle - $arrowAngle)\n    $ay1 = $y2 - $size * [Math]::Sin($angle - $arrowAngle)\n    $ax2 = $x2 - $size * [Math]::Cos($angle + $arrowAngle)\n    $ay2 = $y2 - $size * [Math]::Sin($angle + $arrowAngle)\n    $g.DrawLine($pen, $x2, $y2, $ax1, $ay1)\n    $g.DrawLine($pen, $x2, $y2, $ax2, $ay2)\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Cloud {\n    param($g, $pen, $cx, $cy, $w, $h)\n    Draw-Circle $g $pen ($cx - $w * 0.3) $cy ($h * 0.4)\n    Draw-Circle $g $pen ($cx + $w * 0.1) ($cy - $h * 0.1) ($h * 0.5)\n    Draw-Circle $g $pen ($cx + $w * 0.35) $cy ($h * 0.35)\n}\n\n# 绘制手绘元素\n\n# 左上角 - 装饰性云朵\nDraw-Cloud $g $pen 200 200 200 100\n\n# 左侧 - 大勾选图标\n$checkPen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen($blue, 6)\n$checkPen.EndCap = [System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LineCap]::Round\nDraw-Checkmark $g $checkPen 150 400 80\n\n# 左侧 - 小星星\nDraw-Star $g $pen 100 600 30\nDraw-Star $g $thinPen 80 680 15\n\n# 中上 - 手绘箭头\nDraw-Arrow $g $pen 800 150 1100 150 30\n\n# 中间 - 装饰性圆圈\nDraw-Circle $g $pen 900 500 120\nDraw-Circle $g $thinPen 900 500 140\n\n# 右侧 - 更多手绘元素\nDraw-Star $g $pen 2100 300 50\nDraw-Checkmark $g $checkPen 2050 450 60\n\n# 右下角 - 云朵\nDraw-Cloud $g $thinPen 2200 1100 150 80\n\n# 左下角 - 箭头\nDraw-Arrow $g $pen 100 1200 400 1100 25\n\n# 添加一些随机的点和短线作为装饰\n$random = New-Object Random\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 30; $i++) {\n    $rx = $random.Next(100, $width - 100)\n    $ry = $random.Next(100, $height - 100)\n    $len = $random.Next(10, 40)\n    $angle = $random.NextDouble() * [Math]::PI * 2\n    \n    $g.DrawLine($thinPen, $rx, $ry, \n        $rx + $len * [Math]::Cos($angle),\n        $ry + $len * [Math]::Sin($angle))\n}\n\n# 绘制简单的手绘表情（笑脸）\nfunction Draw-Smiley {\n    param($g, $pen, $cx, $cy, $r)\n    Draw-Circle $g $pen $cx $cy $r\n    # 眼睛\n    $g.FillEllipse([System.Drawing.Brushes]::Gray, ($cx - $r * 0.3), ($cy - $r * 0.15), 8, 8)\n    $g.FillEllipse([System.Drawing.Brushes]::Gray, ($cx + $r * 0.15), ($cy - $r * 0.15), 8, 8)\n    # 微笑\n    $smileRect = [System.Drawing.Rectangle]::new($cx - $r * 0.4, $cy, [int]($r * 0.8), [int]($r * 0.5))\n    $g.DrawArc($pen, $smileRect, 10, 160)\n}\n\nDraw-Smiley $g $pen 1700 700 60\n\n# 保存\n$outputPath = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-handdrawn.png\"\n$bmp.Save($outputPath, [System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat]::Png)\n\n# 清理\n$g.Dispose()\n$bmp.Dispose()\n\nWrite-Host \"手绘壁纸已创建: $outputPath\" -ForegroundColor Green"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":387,"output":2660,"cacheRead":35072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38119,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773637873736}}
