{"type":"message","id":"b9d5b251","parentId":"7a06d900","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:12:31.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the wallpaper was created. It has:\n- A warm off-white paper-textured background\n- Light grid lines like a notebook\n- Hand-drawn style elements:\n  - Cloud shapes\n  - Checkmarks\n  - Stars\n  - Arrows\n  - Circles\n  - A smiley face\n  - Random decorative lines\n\nThis is more in line with Notion's hand-drawn aesthetic. Now let me set this as the wallpaper.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"壁纸已创建！现在设置为桌面壁纸："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf50f50497d3335436b671cdade63","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 设置手绘壁纸并强制刷新\n$wallpaper = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-handdrawn.png\"\n\n# 设置注册表\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"Wallpaper\" -Value $wallpaper -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"WallpaperStyle\" -Value \"10\" -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"TileWallpaper\" -Value \"0\" -Force\n\nWrite-Host \"注册表已设置\"\n\n# 强制刷新 - 重启 explorer 是最可靠的方法\nStop-Process -Name explorer -Force\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\nStart-Process explorer\n\nWrite-Host \"壁纸已设置，资源管理器已重启\" -ForegroundColor Green"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":162,"output":396,"cacheRead":37888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773637943006}}
