{"type":"message","id":"e24e2f9e","parentId":"c502784e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:12:56.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've set the hand-drawn Notion style wallpaper. Let me wait for user feedback on whether this looks good and matches their expectations for \"Notion hand-drawn style\".\n\nIf the user wants something different, I could:\n1. Create a more simplified version\n2. Add more doodles/elements\n3. Use different colors\n4. Create a dark mode version with hand-drawn elements","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**手绘壁纸已设置完成！**\n\n壁纸包含：\n- 📝 温暖的纸质感背景 + 淡网格线（笔记本风格）\n- ✓ 手绘风格的勾选图标\n- ★ 手绘星星\n- → 手绘箭头\n- ☁️ 云朵装饰\n- 😊 可爱笑脸\n\n**请确认：桌面现在显示的是这个手绘风格的壁纸吗？**\n\n如果这不是你想要的 Notion 手绘风格，告诉我你更喜欢哪种感觉：\n1. **更简约** — 只保留少量线条元素\n2. **更丰富** — 添加更多涂鸦和插画\n3. **深色版** — 黑色背景 + 白色手绘线条\n4. **特定元素** — 比如只要线条/几何形状，不要表情等"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":350,"output":330,"cacheRead":38336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773637962661}}
