{"type":"message","id":"f1313aaf","parentId":"03173aad","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:16:27.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来图片应该是正常的。让我再用另一种方法设置壁纸，确保它正确应用。可能需要直接调用 Windows API 或者用 rundll32。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"图片是正常的。让我用另一种方法强制设置壁纸："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf512e80aa7a86f1f5fb9b1f7f73d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 使用 rundll32 直接设置壁纸\n$wallpaper = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-handdrawn.png\"\n\n# 方法: 使用 cmd 调用\ncmd /c \"reg add `\"HKCU\\Control Panel\\Desktop`\" /v Wallpaper /t REG_SZ /d `\"$wallpaper`\" /f\"\ncmd /c \"reg add `\"HKCU\\Control Panel\\Desktop`\" /v WallpaperStyle /t REG_SZ /d 10 /f\"\ncmd /c \"reg add `\"HKCU\\Control Panel\\Desktop`\" /v TileWallpaper /t REG_SZ /d 0 /f\"\n\n# 强制刷新\nrundll32.exe user32.dll,UpdatePerUserSystemParameters ,1 ,True\n\nWrite-Host \"壁纸设置命令已执行\"\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\nWrite-Host \"请查看桌面壁纸变化\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":162,"output":271,"cacheRead":38592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39025,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638176801}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2edc62b","parentId":"f1313aaf","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:16:30.351Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf512e80aa7a86f1f5fb9b1f7f73d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"�����ɹ���ɡ�\r\r\n�����ɹ���ɡ�\r\r\n�����ɹ���ɡ�\r\r\n��ֽ����������ִ��\n��鿴�����ֽ�仯"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3195,"aggregated":"�����ɹ���ɡ�\r\r\n�����ɹ���ɡ�\r\r\n�����ɹ���ɡ�\r\r\n��ֽ����������ִ��\n��鿴�����ֽ�仯","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773638190350}}
{"type":"message","id":"36dc167a","parentId":"e2edc62b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:17:11.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说壁纸还是一团黑的。让我想想可能的原因：\n\n1. 图片确实有问题 - 虽然我看到了预览，但可能在实际显示时有问题\n2. 系统缓存问题\n\n让我创建一个更简单、更可靠的壁纸，使用更基本的方法，确保颜色是可见的。我之前创建的背景色是 #FAF7F2（暖白色），应该是可见的。但可能有问题。\n\n让我创建一个新的壁纸，更简单，直接保存为 24-bit BMP 格式，这是 Windows 最原生支持的壁纸格式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我创建一个更简单可靠的壁纸，直接保存为 BMP 格式（Windows 原生支持）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5131ac3dcb6b5f5423ecb8db8c1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Add-Type -AssemblyName System.Drawing\n\n$width = 1920\n$height = 1080\n\n# 创建画布\n$bmp = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap($width, $height)\n$g = [System.Drawing.Graphics]::FromImage($bmp)\n\n# 背景色 - 温暖的纸白色（RGB: 253, 251, 247）\n$paperWhite = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(253, 251, 247)\n$g.Clear($paperWhite)\n\n# 定义颜色\n$lineColor = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(180, 175, 165)  # 温柔的灰色线条\n$accentBlue = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(90, 140, 180)\n$accentOrange = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(230, 160, 80)\n\n# 画笔\n$pen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen($lineColor, 2.5)\n$bluePen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen($accentBlue, 3)\n$orangePen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen($accentOrange, 2)\n\n# 绘制淡淡的网格线（笔记本风格）\n$gridPen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen([System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(245, 242, 238), 1)\nfor ($x = 0; $x -lt $width; $x += 50) {\n    $g.DrawLine($gridPen, $x, 0, $x, $height)\n}\nfor ($y = 0; $y -lt $height; $y += 50) {\n    $g.DrawLine($gridPen, 0, $y, $width, $y)\n}\n\n# 手绘函数\nfunction Draw-SketchyLine {\n    param($g, $pen, $x1, $y1, $x2, $y2)\n    $points = [System.Collections.Generic.List[System.Drawing.PointF]]::new()\n    $steps = 15\n    $rand = [Random]::new()\n    for ($i = 0; $i -le $steps; $i++) {\n        $t = $i / $steps\n        $x = $x1 + ($x2 - $x1) * $t\n        $y = $y1 + ($y2 - $y1) * $t + $rand.Next(-2, 3)\n        $points.Add([System.Drawing.PointF]::new($x, $y))\n    }\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $points.ToArray())\n}\n\nfunction Draw-SketchyCircle {\n    param($g, $pen, $cx, $cy, $r)\n    $points = [System.Collections.Generic.List[System.Drawing.PointF]]::new()\n    $rand = [Random]::new()\n    for ($i = 0; $i -le 36; $i++) {\n        $angle = [Math]::PI * 2 * $i / 36\n        $rr = $r + $rand.Next(-3, 4)\n        $x = $cx + $rr * [Math]::Cos($angle)\n        $y = $cy + $rr * [Math]::Sin($angle)\n        $points.Add([System.Drawing.PointF]::new($x, $y))\n    }\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $points.ToArray())\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Check {\n    param($g, $pen, $x, $y, $size)\n    $pts = @(\n        [System.Drawing.Point]::new($x, $y + $size * 0.4),\n        [System.Drawing.Point]::new($x + $size * 0.35, $y + $size),\n        [System.Drawing.Point]::new($x + $size, $y)\n    )\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $pts)\n}\n\nfunction Draw-Star4 {\n    param($g, $pen, $cx, $cy, $r)\n    $pts = @()\n    for ($i = 0; $i -lt 8; $i++) {\n        $angle = [Math]::PI * 2 * $i / 8\n        $rr = if ($i % 2 -eq 0) { $r } else { $r * 0.4 }\n        $pts += [System.Drawing.PointF]::new($cx + $rr * [Math]::Cos($angle), $cy + $rr * [Math]::Sin($angle))\n    }\n    $pts += $pts[0]\n    $g.DrawLines($pen, $pts)\n}\n\n# 左上角 - 勾选\nDraw-Check $g $bluePen 120 180 70\n\n# 左侧 - 圆圈\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $pen 180 450 80\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $bluePen 180 450 55\n\n# 左下角 - 星星\nDraw-Star4 $g $orangePen 150 850 35\n\n# 右上角 - 装饰线条\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $pen ($width - 300) 150 ($width - 100) 150\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $pen ($width - 280) 180 ($width - 120) 180\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $pen ($width - 250) 210 ($width - 150) 210\n\n# 右侧 - 小圆圈组\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $pen ($width - 200) 450 40\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $pen ($width - 280) 480 30\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $bluePen ($width - 150) 520 25\n\n# 右下角 - 勾选\nDraw-Check $g $orangePen ($width - 280) 900 50\n\n# 中间偏左 - 大装饰圆\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $pen 450 550 150\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $pen 450 550 120\nDraw-SketchyCircle $g $bluePen 450 550 90\n\n# 中间 - 手绘线条组\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $pen 600 300 800 320\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $pen 620 350 850 330\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $bluePen 650 400 900 380\n\n# 中间偏右 - 星星\nDraw-Star4 $g $pen 1100 600 45\n\n# 底部中间 - 装饰\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $pen 700 ($height - 200) 1000 ($height - 180)\nDraw-SketchyLine $g $orangePen 750 ($height - 150) 950 ($height - 160)\nDraw-Check $g $bluePen 1100 ($height - 220) 45\n\n# 散落的小点装饰\n$rand = [Random]::new()\n$dotBrush = New-Object System.Drawing.SolidBrush($lineColor)\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 25; $i++) {\n    $dx = $rand.Next(100, $width - 100)\n    $dy = $rand.Next(100, $height - 100)\n    $g.FillEllipse($dotBrush, $dx, $dy, 4, 4)\n}\n\n# 保存为 PNG\n$pngPath = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.png\"\n$bmp.Save($pngPath, [System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat]::Png)\n\n# 同时保存为 BMP（Windows 原生支持）\n$bmpPath = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.bmp\"\n$bmp.Save($bmpPath, [System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat]::Bmp)\n\n$g.Dispose()\n$bmp.Dispose()\n\nWrite-Host \"壁纸已创建:\"\nWrite-Host \"PNG: $pngPath\"\nWrite-Host \"BMP: $bmpPath\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":323,"output":2032,"cacheRead":38720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638190353}}
{"type":"message","id":"5bfebf2f","parentId":"36dc167a","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:17:12.581Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf5131ac3dcb6b5f5423ecb8db8c1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"��ֽ�Ѵ���:\nPNG: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.png\nBMP: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.bmp"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1372,"aggregated":"��ֽ�Ѵ���:\nPNG: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.png\nBMP: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.bmp","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773638232580}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4a07db3","parentId":"5bfebf2f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:17:22.172Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有两张壁纸了，一张PNG和一张BMP。让我用BMP格式来设置，因为BMP是Windows原生支持的壁纸格式，不会有任何兼容性问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf513b781404fa4de62c5742a6c4e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 使用 BMP 格式设置壁纸（Windows 原生支持，最可靠）\n$wallpaper = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-sketch.bmp\"\n\n# 设置注册表\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"Wallpaper\" -Value $wallpaper -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"WallpaperStyle\" -Value \"6\" -Force  # 拉伸\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"TileWallpaper\" -Value \"0\" -Force\n\n# 使用 RUNDLL32 强制设置\n$rundllCmd = \"rundll32.exe user32.dll,UpdatePerUserSystemParameters\"\nInvoke-Expression $rundllCmd\n\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 1\nInvoke-Expression $rundllCmd\n\n# 验证\n$wp = Get-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name Wallpaper\nWrite-Host \"当前壁纸路径: $($wp.Wallpaper)\"\n\n# 显示文件信息\n$file = Get-Item $wallpaper\nWrite-Host \"文件大小: $($file.Length / 1KB) KB\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"壁纸已设置为 BMP 格式（纸白色背景 + 手绘涂鸦）\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":1979,"output":374,"cacheRead":39040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41393,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638232582}}
