{"type":"message","id":"79b14f8f","parentId":"d1a60a69","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:17:58.801Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来图片可能没有正确显示。让我试着换一种更可靠的方式来创建壁纸。也许直接用纯色+简单图形会更可靠。\n\n让我创建一个非常简单但可靠的壁纸：纯白色背景上画一些简单的黑色线条，保存为标准格式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我创建一个更简单直接的壁纸，确保颜色正确显示："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf514057764d1dcee95cca8efa293","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 创建极简的 Notion 手绘风壁纸\nAdd-Type -AssemblyName System.Drawing\n\n$bmp = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap(1920, 1080)\n$g = [System.Drawing.Graphics]::FromImage($bmp)\n$g.Clear([System.Drawing.Color]::White)  # 纯白色背景\n\n# 创建画笔 - 使用标准黑色\n$blackPen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen([System.Drawing.Color]::Black, 2)\n$grayPen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen([System.Drawing.Color]::Gray, 1)\n$bluePen = New-Object System.Drawing.Pen([System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(70, 130, 180), 3)  # 钢蓝色\n\n# 画淡淡的网格\nfor ($x = 0; $x -lt 1920; $x += 60) {\n    $g.DrawLine($grayPen, $x, 0, $x, 1080)\n}\nfor ($y = 0; $y -lt 1080; $y += 60) {\n    $g.DrawLine($grayPen, 0, $y, 1920, $y)\n}\n\n# 手绘圆圈 - 左上\n$g.DrawEllipse($blackPen, 150, 150, 120, 120)\n$g.DrawEllipse($bluePen, 170, 170, 80, 80)\n\n# 手绘勾号 - 左中\n$points1 = @(`\n    [System.Drawing.Point]::new(130, 420),`\n    [System.Drawing.Point]::new(160, 460),`\n    [System.Drawing.Point]::new(220, 380)`)\n$g.DrawLines($bluePen, $points1)\n\n# 星星 - 左下\n$starPoints = @()\n$cx, $cy = 180, 800\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 5; $i++) {\n    $angle = [Math]::PI * 2 * $i / 5 - [Math]::PI / 2\n    $starPoints += [System.Drawing.Point]::new([int]($cx + 40 * [Math]::Cos($angle)), [int]($cy + 40 * [Math]::Sin($angle)))\n    $angle2 = $angle + [Math]::PI / 5\n    $starPoints += [System.Drawing.Point]::new([int]($cx + 18 * [Math]::Cos($angle2)), [int]($cy + 18 * [Math]::Sin($angle2)))\n}\n$starPoints += $starPoints[0]\n$g.DrawLines($blackPen, $starPoints)\n\n# 线条组 - 右上\n$g.DrawLine($blackPen, 1600, 150, 1800, 150)\n$g.DrawLine($blackPen, 1620, 180, 1780, 180)\n$g.DrawLine($blackPen, 1650, 210, 1750, 210)\n\n# 圆圈组 - 右中\n$g.DrawEllipse($blackPen, 1700, 480, 80, 80)\n$g.DrawEllipse($blackPen, 1750, 520, 50, 50)\n$g.DrawEllipse($bluePen, 1650, 550, 40, 40)\n\n# 勾号 - 右下\n$points2 = @(`\n    [System.Drawing.Point]::new(1680, 850),`\n    [System.Drawing.Point]::new(1710, 900),`\n    [System.Drawing.Point]::new(1800, 780)`)\n$g.DrawLines($bluePen, $points2)\n\n# 中间大圆\n$g.DrawEllipse($blackPen, 500, 400, 200, 200)\n$g.DrawEllipse($blackPen, 530, 430, 140, 140)\n$g.DrawEllipse($bluePen, 560, 460, 80, 80)\n\n# 中央星星\n$starPoints2 = @()\n$cx2, $cy2 = 1000, 540\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 5; $i++) {\n    $angle = [Math]::PI * 2 * $i / 5 - [Math]::PI / 2\n    $starPoints2 += [System.Drawing.Point]::new([int]($cx2 + 50 * [Math]::Cos($angle)), [int]($cy2 + 50 * [Math]::Sin($angle)))\n    $angle2 = $angle + [Math]::PI / 5\n    $starPoints2 += [System.Drawing.Point]::new([int]($cx2 + 22 * [Math]::Cos($angle2)), [int]($cy2 + 22 * [Math]::Sin($angle2)))\n}\n$starPoints2 += $starPoints2[0]\n$g.DrawLines($blackPen, $starPoints2)\n\n# 底部线条\n$g.DrawLine($blackPen, 600, 900, 1100, 900)\n$g.DrawLine($bluePen, 700, 940, 1000, 940)\n$g.DrawLine($blackPen, 750, 980, 950, 980)\n\n# 保存\n$path = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-doodle.bmp\"\n$bmp.Save($path, [System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat]::Bmp)\n\n$g.Dispose()\n$bmp.Dispose()\n\nWrite-Host \"极简手绘壁纸已创建: $path\"\n(Test-Item $path).Length"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":113,"output":1360,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42881,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638248642}}
