{"type":"message","id":"bbf3ab8e","parentId":"de6b89a5","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:18:51.296Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"BMP 文件是二进制的，无法作为文本读取。让我换一个方式验证图片，并设置它作为壁纸。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5151703dd36788f917e58da18b7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 设置新壁纸\n$wallpaper = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-doodle.bmp\"\n\n# 设置注册表\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"Wallpaper\" -Value $wallpaper -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"WallpaperStyle\" -Value \"6\" -Force\nSet-ItemProperty -Path \"HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop\" -Name \"TileWallpaper\" -Value \"0\" -Force\n\n# 用 SystemParametersInfo 直接设置\nAdd-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\n\npublic class SysParam {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\", EntryPoint=\"SystemParametersInfo\", SetLastError=true)]\n    public static extern bool SetWallpaper(int uAction, int uParam, string lpvParam, int fuWinIni);\n    \n    public static void SetDesktopWallpaper(string path) {\n        SetWallpaper(20, 0, path, 3);\n    }\n}\n\"@\n\n[SysParam]::SetDesktopWallpaper($wallpaper)\n\nWrite-Host \"壁纸设置完成: $wallpaper\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"这是纯白色背景 + 黑色/蓝色手绘涂鸦的壁纸\"\nWrite-Host \"如果还是黑色的，请告诉我\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":154,"output":348,"cacheRead":44224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44726,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773638322096}}
